{"tid":1442350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警係貪污，黑警係貪污，黑警係貪污","createTime":"2019-08-11T02:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T03:53:14.000Z","uid":149785,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c9896578fa005577ca847f26f4105806f201c6d6","tid":1442350,"uid":149785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:39:12.000Z","msg":"其實黑警點草管人命大陸同藍絲都唔會理<br />\n唯獨要指出佢地同黑社會既係貪污，唔係單純勾結<br />\n大陸要打貪，所以一定要講打貪班姓絲藍絲先會面對現實<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警721<br />\n貪污走唔甩</span></span>"},{"pid":"a4eedea5fbbc271227bfddab02d770ed4445bd1c","tid":1442350,"uid":132816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:39:30.000Z","msg":"黑警721<br />\n貪污走唔甩"},{"pid":"010efd94e057f5c01e5c4d7d7a44cb50910fa951","tid":1442350,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:41:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a14958f0f0618fb345599d421827035baf485250","tid":1442350,"uid":149785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:41:58.000Z","msg":"佢地唔係守護法治，係貪緊污呀"},{"pid":"d7090944bef5922c02727a079739cf0ef604fe94","tid":1442350,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:44:02.000Z","msg":"有什麼是抗爭者可做，但還未做的事？X先生說：「第一，我講多次，就係日日打721呢個死穴，因為林鄭同警方依家完全冇得拆。第二，將民建聯同黑警綑綁，要佢哋永不分離。中央撐警，建制派一定要歸隊，冇可能割席。好多人冇留意到北京撐警，其實係一把雙刃劍，好處係穩定軍心，防止警察叛變，壞處係會累死建制派。大家點解唔日日問吓民建聯啲區議員同立法會議員，『你撐唔撐警』、『覺唔覺得警察濫用暴力』呢？記住問是非題，一係yes，一係no，咪畀位佢遊花園呀。」<br />\n<br />\nBy 政界猛人揭林鄭底牌 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"64c55335321e1a7e79b96f57a29e89ff2b3803d8","tid":1442350,"uid":94665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:44:48.000Z","msg":"上面貪下面未必<br />\n不過都要痛腳<br />\n要一齊打"},{"pid":"1a7f51bf38c94554bf240999e03ee95faa910a75","tid":1442350,"uid":149785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546d310163b08239c3d4323009776b53948bbd7f","tid":1442350,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:50:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"06dd38b4c802000ac1f194dd19497be2e382dbdc","tid":1442350,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:53:14.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />721<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />721<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://serving.photos.photobox.com/68162593a7d3462ae87e1f66ff2de58544106d79d4af7fdb96125e69b2c7007b3b497024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fserving.photos.photobox.com%2F68162593a7d3462ae87e1f66ff2de58544106d79d4af7fdb96125e69b2c7007b3b497024.jpg&h=eb87d556&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}